{"tid":2452903,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺童年回憶既漫畫 如果近幾年出新作 一定會比個作者寫到好似惡搞咁","createTime":"2021-03-19T06:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T01:07:35.000Z","uid":42246,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ae6b0ae6f3a334a62775244fe0882ed9963ba46c","tid":2452903,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T06:26:41.000Z","msg":"上次睇完 金田一37歲事件簿<br />\n阿一37歲成件垃圾咁 重未同美雪結婚<br />\n<br />\n龍珠超 由佢開始變藍色紅色 已經覺得唔係同一樣野來<br />\n<br />\nEVA （依套我冇睇） 岩岩睇到佢劇透大結局 明日香又係搞笑既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n火影忍者 由少年向變成兒童向 同當年鋪左悟飯上位 又拉返佢落來一樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時冇事既只有數碼暴龍？"},{"pid":"6acd3731054aadd2be8f1a0379cb6bffd3c7a0b5","tid":2452903,"uid":278184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T06:28:14.000Z","msg":"數碼暴龍tri咪俾人屌到開花囉<br />\n依家新呢套好似好睇返"},{"pid":"ed7095693299804a1ac96a093cdb1c986cb6ea0b","tid":2452903,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T06:28:51.000Z","msg":"寵物小精靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e7f2f1b89f3a9b96b87a48ece754a19288adf18","tid":2452903,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T06:30:33.000Z","msg":"EVA係動畫 港父又柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb67715fd28ffee7dc1dbe0bb19fa734fe85019b","tid":2452903,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed7095693299804a1ac96a093cdb1c986cb6ea0b","tid":2452903,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T06:28:51.000Z","msg":"寵物小精靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T06:30:53.000Z",